  <text>
    <body>
      <u who="A">
        <s>Hi <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Maya</ref>!</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>Hey... what happened with <choice><orig>ur</orig><reg>your</reg></choice> face?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>It's a long story.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>So... will you tell me?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>A few days ago my working partner <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Isaac</ref> and his wife <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Jory</ref> came us to visit.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>Alright.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>I had an affair with <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Isaac</ref> in <name type="geo">London</name>.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>What?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>Yeah, I totally regret it but <choice><orig>can not</orig><reg>cannot</reg></choice> set the time back.</s>
        <s>So when <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Isaac</ref> and <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Jory</ref> came to us, <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Isaac</ref> tried to kiss me and <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Jory</ref> caught us.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>Oh, no!</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>It was so chaotic.</s>
        <s>When the whole argument was over, <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Amir</ref> asked me if I really had an affair with <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Isaac</ref>.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>So what did you do?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>I told him the truth... because I love him.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>So what did he do?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>He... punched... me...</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>HE DID WHAT?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>He punched me multiple times in the face...</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>This son of a bitch...</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>Don't call him that.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>Sorry...?</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>He was controlled by his emotions, he totally regrets it.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>That's not an excuse.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>So what should I do, you also know <ref target="a11lk2_1" type="character">Amir</ref>.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>I think the best thing you both can do is stay away from each other.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>Ok...</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>Maybe you should not report him to the police... because our society is often unfair and as <choice><orig>an</orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Muslim you often have to handle with racist cops or judges.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="A">
        <s>Ok <choice><orig>thats</orig><reg>that's</reg></choice> a good advice, thank you so much.</s>
      </u>
      <u who="B">
        <s>No problem, I'm always there for you.</s>
      </u>
    </body>
